title: Arcturus - La Masquerade Infernale
description:
La Masquerade Infernale Musical Album

La Masquerade Infernale is a 1997 album by Arcturus. 
Released by Misanthropy Records, the album is a huge step away from the slow, doom-influenced melodic black metal of Aspera Hiems Symfonia.
